Package: libpoc0
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Section: libs
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: PoC (Push-to-Talk over Cellular) protocol library
 A C library implementing the signaling and audio transport protocol
 used by PoC radios for group and private push-to-talk over cellular
 networks. Supports Speex audio codec, MS-framed TCP signaling, and
 UDP voice transport.

Package: libpoc-dev
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Section: libdevel
Depends: libpoc0 (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends}
Description: PoC protocol library (development files)
 A C library implementing the signaling and audio transport protocol
 used by PoC radios for group and private push-to-talk over cellular
 networks.
 .
 This package contains the header files and pkg-config file needed
 to build programs that use libpoc.
